{"tid":545132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【親中議員 葛珮帆】浸大事件　文化港獨都是港獨　反大陸化即是港獨","createTime":"2018-01-30T08:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T09:03:34.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c03a2b70af017a02cd0411992a873720a71958b","tid":545132,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180126/00184_006.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180126%2F00184_006.html&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d3c1bfcc\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180126/00184_006.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://eqweb.hk/index.php/eq-channel/eq-channel-sub-1/2299-2018-01-29-08-25-29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feqweb.hk%2Findex.php%2Feq-channel%2Feq-channel-sub-1%2F2299-2018-01-29-08-25-29&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2050be6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://eqweb.hk/index.php/eq-channel/eq-channel-sub-1/2299-2018-01-29-08-25-29</a><br />\n<br />\n浸大佔領事件持續發酵，其實質是有人企圖以「文化」包裝「港獨」。整個佔領行動，是由一個撐粵語、反普通話的團體──「港語學」於語文中心作網上直播。被停學的陳樂行就是「港語學」召集人，有報道指他長期參與、策劃港獨、反中、反普等活動。<br />\n<br />\n借反普通話推動「文化港獨」早有前科。一三年，當時的公民黨議員毛孟靜聯同其他反對派議員舉行傳媒茶敍，聲稱所謂「本土語言」已遭全面的「大陸化清洗」。一五年毛再在立法會提出動議，要求政府「保障香港不受『大陸化』」，另有議員伺機提出修正案，要求把擱置「以普通話教授中國語文科」設置成教學的長遠目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員 葛珮帆"},{"pid":"097ea528e24909ac5ede275cebb9f91ce2309078","tid":545132,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://eqweb.hk/images/EQ/channal_pic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Feqweb.hk%2Fimages%2FEQ%2Fchannal_pic.png&h=cd3b7420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91bd067f3ae6597a18662dc6cf21c12941016955","tid":545132,"uid":36901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"假博士你講廣東話！<br />\n港獨分子！！"},{"pid":"0133f1c118a010e